@api_base_url = https://localhost:7123

### Create a memory-backed session
POST {{api_base_url}}/api/memory/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-123",
  "model": "gpt-4o"
}

###

### Send a message (update sessionId from response above)
POST {{api_base_url}}/api/memory/my-memory-session-1/messages?userId=user-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "My favorite programming language is C#. Remember that."
}

###

### Get stored memory for a user
GET {{api_base_url}}/api/memory/user-123

###

### Delete stored memory for a user
DELETE {{api_base_url}}/api/memory/user-123

###
